{"tid":1400404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌撚晒前線同冷氣軍師","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:57:23.000Z","uid":243854,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f91e6ca36b956e59527835c81ff2f7ca83d854f","tid":1400404,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，前線要屌就淨係屌唔睇情況一味死勇嘅<br />\n不過，呢啲人數應該極少數，至少而家少咗好多因為無腦而送頭(無錯有啲太激動，但請記住有時保護自己最重要)，反而係為咗中後嘅人走先守<br />\n<br />\n但係，屌你老母，冷氣軍師你哋做乜撚咗開個POST就咁叫人走？<br />\n無錯，喺電腦前睇直播會對大局了解更多<br />\n但係唔撚使乜撚都無講就叫人走，相反你係分析晒同埋講晒啲情況畀前線，等前線決定走唔走<br />\n而唔撚係一句快走，仲喺度做乜呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70af7f5bee76d40f4158d921f3113d6622f6096","tid":1400404,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"負乜撚嘢評呀㗎屌你老母"},{"pid":"775639150a90857906a0573807d7a63ee354e236","tid":1400404,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:48:39.000Z","msg":"睇撚晒先評啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"dc6123d59926ecd93058ff9431624677a17490e5","tid":1400404,"uid":243854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母成班冷氣軍師淨係識負評？"},{"pid":"739aa61be3b84821b07a86c18eb0ae85ddc1bf4f","tid":1400404,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"其實係要推逃生資訊同對方佈防畀前線，之後就由現場人士決定"},{"pid":"46df2ae7b3f50e37748ebb9ca6cbafc3e57723f9","tid":1400404,"uid":243854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"739aa61be3b84821b07a86c18eb0ae85ddc1bf4f","tid":1400404,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"其實係要推逃生資訊同對方佈防畀前線，之後就由現場人士決定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"而家咪屌啲垃圾一句就叫人走囉<br />\n乜撚都唔講清楚就叫人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6f75fab237690d86ecdcbf3a41ed9dfc6d4bd9","tid":1400404,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:56:19.000Z","msg":"分化？"},{"pid":"192d0d3387c2ab1a070d60bb4535b1cdd168d440","tid":1400404,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6f75fab237690d86ecdcbf3a41ed9dfc6d4bd9","tid":1400404,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:56:19.000Z","msg":"分化？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1400361/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1400361/page/1</a><br />\n睇下呢個POST做乜撚嘢"}]}